Bowl Body: A semi-spherical or conical shape.
Parameters: body_height=80, body_bottom_radius=100, body_top_radius=125
Orientation: body_origin=(0,0,0), body_normal=ZAxis

Bowl Base: A flat surface in a circular shape at the bottom of the bowl.
Parameters: base_radius=body_bottom_radius
Orientation: base_origin=body_origin, base_normal=body_normal